    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A – H. Tropidoturris vizcondei sp. nov. A – B. Holotype (MNHN 26614), 11.1 x 4.3 mm. C – H. Paratype (MZB 60071). C. Shell, scale bar 1 mm. D. Penultimate whorl, scale bar 500 µm. E. Surface microsculpture, scale bar 40 µm. F – G. Protoconch, scale bar 200 µm. H. Microsculpture of protoconch, scale bar 100 µm. I – K. Iredalea adenensis sp. nov. I – J. Holotype (MZB 60072), 17.2 x 7.7 mm. K. Penultimate whorl. L – P. Buchema shearmani sp. nov. L – M. Holotype (MZB 60073), 9.9 x 3.5 mm. O. Protoconch. P. Detail of penultimate whorl. Q – S. Crassispira somalica sp. nov. Q – R. Holotype (MZB 60076), 21 x 8.9 mm. S. Penultimate whorl." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220155/files/figure.png" ;
